Subject: Estimate Request Acknowledgment - {{address}}
Body:
Hello {{agentName}},

Thank you for reaching out to us and asking us to bid on your project at {{address}}. We are excited about the possibility of working with you.

An account executive will reach out shortly to schedule a walkthrough, either on-site or virtual, at your convenience.

To make our call more effective and help us better prepare, we kindly request your assistance in answering the following questions:

  • What is the “as is” price comps show the property could list at?
  • What is the “after repair/staged” price comps show the property could list at?
  • What is the target price the homeowner wants to list at?
  • What is the target price the homeowner wants to pay for repair/staging?
  • How much is owed on the property?
  • What is the owners credit score? (We don’t pull this, we need in writing)
  • When does the homeowner want to sell the property?
  • Please provide us with a clean title.

Additionally, please use this link to access a private folder where you can upload any pictures, videos, or documents that can assist us in scoping the project. You can upload media using mobile devices or a desktop computer.

Summary of the request:

  • Address: {{address}}
  • Agent: {{agentName}}
  • Agent Phone: {{agentPhone}}
  • Agent Email: {{agentEmail}}
  • Owner: {{first}} {{last}}
  • Owner Phone: {{phone}}
  • OwnerEmail: {{email}}
  • Relation: {{relation}}
  • Brokerage: {{lead}}
  • Need Finance: {{finance}}
  • Preferred Realtech Digital: {{digital}}
  • Notes: {{note}}

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this quote, please don’t hesitate to get in touch with us at office@realtechee.com.

Sincerely,
The RealTechee Team
